# HTML standards

- One `<h1>` per page; no skipped heading levels
- Use `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<footer>`, `<section>` — not div soup
- One `<main>` per page
- ARIA only when native HTML is insufficient
- Every `<img>` has `alt`; decorative = `alt=""`
- Set `width` and `height` on images
- `lang="en"` on `<html>`
- Include meta description + Open Graph on index pages
- Skip link to `#main`; `:focus-visible` on interactive elements
- Validate: `npx html-validate "**/*.html"`
